_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made soft cotton jumpsuit with hood
_xResult.longdesc:
This custom made jumpsuit will be your go-to throw on piece for the new season. Featuring a front zipper, two pockets and a big hood, this made to measure piece is super comfortable and easy to wear. The wide legs and loose style provide a chic and edgy look, whether you pair it with sneakers or wedges.

 

Have fun with EUG's custom made designer clothing! For custom made requests regarding sizing, let the designer know using the button below.
